CustomFunction.Calculation:
// ValueIsInList (someValueList, someValue )
// version 1.2, Erik Shagdar, Dan Shockley, NYHTC

/*
	Simple test to be sure a VALUE is in a list using an exact match. 


HISTORY:
	1.2 - 2016-09-29 ( eshagdar ): updated documentation.
	1.1 - 201x-xx-xx ( eshagdar ): uses Position instead of patternCount for slightly faster performance
	1.0 - 201x-xx-xx ( dshockley ): first created.
*/


Position ( "¶" & someValueList & "¶"; "¶" & someValue & "¶"; 1; 1 ) > 0
